name: NomadicAmbience-VideoSkill
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nomadic ambience
des:
Want to go for a ride, Just ask Alexa, open nomadic ambience. The skill will play videos of a person walking in the streets in the rain and snowfall of the United States and Easter Countries. Go on a ride with the skill.

You can play the skill on all Echo Display devices:
Echo Display devices
Firestick TV
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
